# ACTUALIZO un PRODUCTO EXISTENTE COMO ADMINISTRADOR
PUT http://localhost:3000/admin/products/update/6
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: bearer <token>

{
    "price": 500.00
}

###

# ELIMINO UN PRODUCTO EXISTENTE COMO ADMINISTRADOR
DELETE http://localhost:3000/admin/products/delete/6
Authorization: bearer <token>